 2690        private void RefreshTxtContent(ClinicalNoteDocumentDetails objNoteDocumentDetails, UTF8Encoding enc)
 2691        {
 02692            string txtData = enc.GetString(objNoteDocumentDetails.Content);
 02693            CDocProdInput objCResoving = new CDocProdInput();
 02694            DocumentProduction cnsProduction = new DocumentProduction();
 02695            byte[] bcontent = null;
 02696            objCResoving.TemplateInfo = base.WizardContext;
 02697            objCResoving.TemplateInfo["CURREncounterOID"] = PageState.GetValue("EncounterOID");
 02698            cnsProduction.FillContextinformations(ref objCResoving);
 2699
 02700            string sPatientOID = PageState.GetValue("PatientOID");
 02701             if (DocumentProduction.IsPatientSensitive(sPatientOID) && !Clnhelpler.IsPatientSensitiveOverrided())
 02702                objCResoving.ResolveRestricted = false;
 2703            else
 02704                objCResoving.ResolveRestricted = true;
 02705             if (objCResoving.TemplateInfo != null && objCResoving.TemplateInfo["DTMPRODUCTION"] == "TRUE")
 02706                cnsProduction.filDocprdobjectEx(objCResoving.TemplateInfo, ref objCResoving);
 02707            string sDistrCont = PageState.GetValue("DISTRLIST");
 02708             if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(sDistrCont))
 02709                objCResoving.TemplateInfo["PRDDistributionList"] = PageState.GetValue("DISTRLIST");
 2710
 02711             if (objNoteDocumentDetails.ClinicalNoteDocumentInfo != null)
 02712                cnsProduction.SetDistributionListIfReqd(objCResoving, objNoteDocumentDetails.ClinicalNoteDocumentInfo.Cl
 02713            cnsProduction.ResolveDocForAutoRefresh(objCResoving, txtData, out bcontent);
 02714            objNoteDocumentDetails.Content = bcontent;
 02715        }
